    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A type of German glass jug that is onion-shaped and has a neck or spout formed of several intertwined tubes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
